title: Delays on A38(M) Aston Expressway after accident
text:
There is very slow traffic on the A48(M) Aston Expressway outbound in Birmingham after an accident between A38 Aston Road / A4540 Newtown Middleway (Dartmouth Circus) and B4132 Waterlinks Boulevard / Victoria Road (Park Circus).
The accident happened at around 5:35pm. One lane is blocked.
Last updated Wed 9 Sep 2015 Travel Birmingham Aston Expressway West Midlands
